<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>생활기록부 스마트 점검 프로그램</title>
  <!-- Pretendard Web Font CDN -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <!-- SheetJS CDN (Excel parsing and exporting) -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xlsx-js-style@1.2.0/dist/xlsx.bundle.js"></script>
  <!-- Lucide Icons CDN -->
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <div id="app-container">
    
    <!-- Sidebar Navigation (Notion style) -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; width: 100%;">
        <div class="sidebar-brand-wrapper" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap;">
          <span class="sidebar-logo">📝</span>
          <span class="sidebar-title">생기부 점검기</span>
        </div>
        <button id="btn-toggle-main-sidebar" class="btn-icon" title="메뉴 접기/펼치기" style="border: none; background: none; padding: 4px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
          <i data-lucide="menu" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <nav class="sidebar-menu">
        <div class="menu-item active" data-tab="data-management">
          <i data-lucide="database"></i>
          <span>데이터 관리</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item" data-tab="student-group-view">
          <i data-lucide="users"></i>
          <span>학생별 확인</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item" data-tab="subject-group-view">
          <i data-lucide="book-open"></i>
          <span>과목별 확인</span>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item" data-tab="settings">
          <i data-lucide="settings"></i>
          <span>점검 규칙 설정</span>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <div class="sidebar-footer">
        <p>생활기록부 점검 v1.0</p>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Main Content Area -->
    <main class="content-area">
      
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <header class="page-header">
        <h2 class="page-title" id="current-page-title">
          <i data-lucide="database"></i>
          <span>데이터 관리</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="page-actions" id="header-actions">
          <!-- Contextual buttons will load here -->
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- TAB 1: DATA MANAGEMENT -->
      <div id="data-management" class="tab-content active">
        <div class="data-tab-wrapper">
          
          <!-- Statistics Widget Dashboard -->
          <div class="dashboard-summary">
            <div class="summary-card">
              <span class="summary-label">전체 학생 수</span>
              <span class="summary-value" id="stats-total-students">0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-card">
              <span class="summary-label">전체 기록(행) 수</span>
              <span class="summary-value" id="stats-checked-students">0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-card">
              <span class="summary-label">검출된 오류 수</span>
              <span class="summary-value" id="stats-total-errors">0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-card">
              <span class="summary-label">기재 금지 위반 수</span>
              <span class="summary-value" id="stats-forbidden-errors">0</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Excel Drag & Drop Upload Zone -->
          <div class="upload-zone" id="excel-upload-zone">
            <i data-lucide="upload-cloud"></i>
            <h3>엑셀(XLSX / CSV) 파일 업로드</h3>
            <p>여기로 파일을 드래그하거나 클릭하여 파일을 선택해 주세요.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-light);">
              (학년도, 학기, 학번, 이름, 과목명, 내용 항목이 포함된 엑셀을 업로드하세요)
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Table Controls (Search, Add Row, Sample Download) -->
          <div class="table-controls">
            <div class="search-box">
              <i data-lucide="search"></i>
              <input type="text" id="student-search-input" placeholder="이름, 학번, 과목 검색...">
            </div>
            
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
              <button class="btn btn-danger" id="btn-delete-selected" style="display: none; background-color: var(--color-spelling-bg); color: var(--color-spelling-text); border-color: rgba(212,64,39,0.15);">
                <i data-lucide="trash-2"></i>
                <span>선택 삭제</span>
              </button>
              <button class="btn" id="btn-download-sample">
                <i data-lucide="download"></i>
                <span>양식 다운로드</span>
              </button>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-add-row">
                <i data-lucide="plus"></i>
                <span>학생 추가</span>
              </button>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-inspect-all-nav">
                <i data-lucide="sparkles"></i>
                <span>일괄 분석</span>
              </button>
              <button class="btn" id="btn-export-errors-excel" style="background-color: var(--color-slang-bg); color: var(--color-slang-text); border-color: rgba(179,89,0,0.15);">
                <i data-lucide="file-warning"></i>
                <span>수정 요청 다운로드</span>
              </button>
              <button class="btn" id="btn-export-excel">
                <i data-lucide="file-output"></i>
                <span>엑셀 저장</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Notion-like Filter & Sort Toolbar -->
          <div class="filter-toolbar" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; align-items: center; padding: 10px 0; margin-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); font-size: 13px;">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
              <i data-lucide="filter" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary);"></i>
              <span style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary);">필터:</span>
            </div>
            
            <select id="filter-year" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
              <option value="all">학년: 전체</option>
            </select>
            
            <select id="filter-class" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
              <option value="all">반: 전체</option>
            </select>

            <select id="filter-subject" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
              <option value="all">과목/활동: 전체</option>
            </select>

            <div style="margin-left: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
              <i data-lucide="arrow-up-down" style="width: 14px; height: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary);"></i>
              <span style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary);">정렬:</span>
              <select id="sort-criteria" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; width: 145px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                <option value="sNum-asc">학번 순 (오름차순)</option>
                <option value="sNum-desc">학번 순 (내림차순)</option>
                <option value="name-asc">이름 순</option>
                <option value="subject-asc">과목 순</option>
                <option value="errors-desc">오류 많은 순</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Excel Database Grid -->
          <div class="table-wrapper">
            <table class="notion-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th style="width: 30px; text-align: center;"><input type="checkbox" id="th-select-all"></th>
                  <th style="width: 50px;">구분</th>
                  <th style="width: 70px;">학년도</th>
                  <th style="width: 50px;">학기</th>
                  <th style="width: 80px;">학번</th>
                  <th style="width: 90px;">이름</th>
                  <th style="width: 120px;">과목명 / 주제명</th>
                  <th>내용 (생활기록부 세부 특기사항)</th>
                  <th style="width: 120px;">검출 오류</th>
                  <th style="width: 80px;">작업</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="student-table-body">
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="10" style="text-align: center; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 32px 0;">
                    <i data-lucide="info" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 4px; display: inline-block;"></i>
                    등록된 학생 데이터가 없습니다. 직접 추가하거나 엑셀 파일을 업로드해 주세요.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <!-- Pagination Bar -->
          <div class="pagination-bar" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 12px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              <span>페이지당 표시 행 수:</span>
              <select id="select-rows-per-page" class="editor-input" style="padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 12px; height: 26px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                <option value="20">20개</option>
                <option value="30" selected>30개</option>
                <option value="50">50개</option>
                <option value="100">100개</option>
                <option value="all">모두 보기</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-prev-page" style="padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 26px;">
                <i data-lucide="chevron-left" style="width:12px; height:12px; vertical-align: middle;"></i>
                <span style="vertical-align: middle;">이전</span>
              </button>
              <span id="txt-page-info" style="font-weight: 500;">1 / 1 페이지</span>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-next-page" style="padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 26px;">
                <span style="vertical-align: middle;">다음</span>
                <i data-lucide="chevron-right" style="width:12px; height:12px; vertical-align: middle;"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- TAB 2: STUDENT GROUP VIEW (점검 에디터 통합) -->
      <div id="student-group-view" class="tab-content">
        <div class="split-container">
          
          <!-- 좌측: 대상 학생 명부 사이드바 (320px) -->
          <div class="sidebar-student-list">
            <div style="padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; position: relative;">
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                <span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-primary);">대상 학생 <span id="editor-student-count" style="color: var(--color-slang-text); font-weight:700;">0</span>명</span>
                <button id="btn-collapse-student-list" class="btn-icon" title="목록 접기" style="border: none; background: none; padding: 4px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <i data-lucide="chevrons-left" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
                </button>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 학생 이름 검색 -->
              <div class="search-box" style="margin-top: 4px;">
                <i data-lucide="search"></i>
                <input type="text" id="editor-student-search" placeholder="학생 이름 검색..." style="font-size:12px;">
              </div>
              
              <!-- 학년/반 단일 필터 콤보 -->
              <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px; margin-top: 4px;">
                <select id="editor-student-filter-year" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                  <option value="all">전체 학년</option>
                </select>
                <select id="editor-student-filter-class" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 12px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                  <option value="all">전체 반</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 오류 감출 학생 필터 체크박스 -->
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 6px; padding: 2px 4px;">
                <input type="checkbox" id="editor-student-filter-error-only" style="cursor: pointer; width: 14px; height: 14px;">
                <label for="editor-student-filter-error-only" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer; user-select: none; font-weight: 500;">
                  오류 검출된 학생만 보기
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 세로 학생 리스트 (스크롤) -->
            <div id="editor-student-list-container" style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 6px;">
              <!-- 학생 아이템들이 동적으로 빌드됨 -->
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 우측: 에디터 및 오류 검사 영역 -->
          <div class="editor-main-area">
            
            <!-- 대기 상태 (선택된 학생이 없을 때 표시) -->
            <div id="editor-empty-state" style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: center; padding: 32px;">
              <i data-lucide="file-search" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; color: var(--border-focus); margin-bottom: 12px;"></i>
              <h4 style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text-primary);">선택된 학생 없음</h4>
              <p style="font-size: 13px; max-width: 320px;">좌측 명부에서 작성 및 점검할 학생을 선택해 주세요.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 실제 편집 본문 (학생 선택 시 활성화) -->
            <div id="editor-active-container" class="inspection-container" style="display: none;">
              
              <!-- Left side: Content Editor -->
              <div class="editor-panel">
                <div class="student-selector-bar" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; width: 100%;">
                  <div class="student-info-tag" style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <button id="btn-expand-student-list" class="btn-icon" title="목록 펼치기" style="display: none; border: none; background: none; padding: 5px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
                      <i data-lucide="chevrons-right" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
                    </button>
                    <strong id="current-student-name" style="font-size:16px;">학생 선택 없음</strong>
                    <span id="current-student-meta" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 8px;"></span>
                  </div>
                  <!-- 이전/다음 학생 이동 및 결과 펼치기 버튼 영역 -->
                  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                    <div class="student-nav-buttons" style="display: flex; gap: 4px;">
                      <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-prev-student" style="padding: 4px 8px; height: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-left" style="width:14px; height:14px;"></i>
                      </button>
                      <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btn-next-student" style="padding: 4px 8px; height: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                        <i data-lucide="chevron-right" style="width:14px; height:14px;"></i>
                      </button>
                    </div>
                    <button id="btn-expand-results-panel" class="btn-icon" title="결과 펼치기" style="display: none; border: none; background: none; padding: 5px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-secondary); height: 30px; width: 30px;">
                      <i data-lucide="chevrons-left" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Editor Fields (Readonly Meta + Editable Textarea) -->
                <div class="editor-body-wrapper" style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; padding: 16px;">
                  <div class="editor-field-group" style="display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <span class="editor-label" style="width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">怨쇰ぉ / ?쒕룞紐?/span>
                    
                    <!-- 援먭낵 ?좏깮 ?쒕∼?ㅼ슫 -->
                    <select id="editor-subject-select" class="editor-input" style="flex: 1; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; padding: 4px 8px; font-size:13px; height:32px; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text-primary);">
                      <!-- ?곗씠??怨쇰ぉ 紐⑸줉 + [吏곸젒 ?낅젰...] -->
                    </select>

                    <!-- 吏곸젒 ?낅젰???명뭼 -->
                    <input type="text" id="editor-subject-direct-input" class="editor-input" style="display: none; flex: 1; height:32px; font-size:13px;" placeholder="怨쇰ぉ紐낆쓣 吏곸젒 ?낅젰?섏꽭??>
                  </div>

                  <!-- ?대떦 援먯궗 ?낅젰 ?꾨뱶 -->
                  <div class="editor-field-group" style="display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <span class="editor-label" style="width: 80px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">?대떦 援먯궗</span>
                    <input type="text" id="editor-teacher-input" class="editor-input" style="flex: 1; height:32px; font-size:13px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; padding: 4px 8px; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text-primary);" placeholder="?대떦 援먯궗紐낆쓣 ?낅젰?섏꽭??(?? 源援?뼱)">
                  </div>

                  <!-- Highlighting Textarea -->
                  <div class="editor-text-container" style="flex: 1; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                    <div id="editable-content" class="editor-textarea" contenteditable="true" spellcheck="false" style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; outline: none; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px; font-size:14px; line-height: 1.6; background-color: var(--bg-primary); min-height: 200px;"></div>
                  </div>

                  <!-- ?섏젙 ?붿껌?ы빆 硫붿떊? 蹂듭궗 ?≪뀡 ?곸뿭 -->
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <button id="btn-copy-request-message" class="btn btn-primary" style="flex: 1; justify-content: center; height: 38px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; gap: 8px;">
                      <i data-lucide="send" style="width: 15px; height: 15px;"></i>
                      ?대떦 ?좎깮?섍퍡 ?꾩넚???섏젙 ?붿껌 ?ы빆 蹂듭궗
                    </button>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Footer with Byte Counter -->
                  <div class="editor-footer" style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                    <span style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-light);">* 蹂몃Ц 媛뺤“ ?⑥뼱瑜??대┃?섎㈃ ?곗륫 移대뱶濡?諛붾줈 ?대룞?⑸땲??</span>
                    <div class="byte-counter">
                      <span>湲???? <strong id="char-count">0</strong>??/span>
                      <span>NEIS 諛붿씠?? <strong id="byte-count" class="byte-badge">0</strong> / 1500 Byte</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Right side: Error Inspection Results Panel -->
              <div class="results-panel" style="width: 320px; flex-shrink: 0; border-left: 1px solid var(--border-color); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                <div class="results-header">
                  <div class="results-title">
                    <i data-lucide="alert-circle"></i>
                    <span>諛쒓껄???ㅻ쪟 諛?嫄댁쓽?ы빆</span>
                    <span class="results-count-badge" id="errors-count-badge">0</span>
                  </div>
                  <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-apply-all-fixes" style="padding: 4px 8px; font-size: 12px;">
                    <i data-lucide="sparkles"></i>
                    <span>紐⑤뱺 ?쒖븞 ?곸슜</span>
                  </button>
                </div>

                <div class="results-list" id="inspection-results-list" style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto;">
                  <!-- Result cards will render here -->
                  <div class="empty-state">
                    <i data-lucide="check-circle"></i>
                    <h4>寃異쒕맂 ?ㅻ쪟 ?놁쓬</h4>
                    <p>留욎땄踰?諛?湲곗옱 吏移⑥뿉 ?닿툔?섎뒗 ?ㅻ쪟媛 諛쒓껄?섏? ?딆븯?듬땲??</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div> <!-- editor-active-container ?ロ옒 -->
          </div> <!-- editor-main-area ?ロ옒 -->
        </div> <!-- split-container ?ロ옒 -->
      </div> <!-- inspection-editor ???ロ옒 -->

      <!-- TAB 3: SETTINGS -->
      <div id="settings" class="tab-content">
        <div class="settings-tab-wrapper">
          
          <!-- Inspection Rules Toggle -->
          <div class="settings-section">
            <h4 class="settings-section-title">
              <i data-lucide="shield-check"></i>
              <span>?쒖꽦?뷀븷 ?먭? 洹쒖튃</span>
            </h4>
            
            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>留욎땄踰?諛??뷀븳 ?ㅽ깉???먭?</h5>
                <p>?앷린遺 ?ㅻ퉰???ㅽ깉????솢, ?щ떎, 臾대궃?섎떎 ??瑜?媛먯??⑸땲??</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-spelling" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>鍮꾪몴以??諛?泥?냼??????ъ슜 湲덉?</h5>
                <p>?밸컺?? 媛쒖씠?? ?쇰?????寃⑹떇 ?녿뒗 ???諛??좏뻾?대? ?먭??⑸땲??</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-slang" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>?몃옒???쒓린 援먯젙</h5>
                <p>?쒕Ъ?덉씠??-> ?쒕??덉씠?????섎せ ?쒓린???몃옒?대? 李얠뒿?덈떎.</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-loanword" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>?곗냽 ?꾩뼱?곌린 ?먭?</h5>
                <p>2媛??댁긽 ?곗냽?쇰줈 ?낅젰??遺덊븘?뷀븳 怨듬갚??1媛쒕줈 以꾩엯?덈떎.</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-spacing" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>臾몄옣 醫낃껐 ?⑥젏(.) ?먭?</h5>
                <p>媛?臾몄옣???앹씠 留덉묠??.)濡??앸굹吏 ?딆? ?ㅻ쪟瑜?泥댄겕?⑸땲??</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-endingDot" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>?앷린遺 湲곗옱 湲덉? ?ㅼ썙???꾪꽣留?/h5>
                <p>?댄븰?깆쟻(?좎씡 ??, 援먯쇅????섏긽?ㅼ쟻, ?ъ꽕湲곌? ?멸툒???쒗븳?⑸땲??</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-forbidden" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="toggle-item">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>?숈깮 蹂몄씤 ?ㅻ챸 ?몄텧 二쇱쓽</h5>
                <p>蹂몃Ц???숈깮 ?ㅻ챸??吏곸젒 ?ㅼ뼱媛붾뒗吏 寃?ы븯???泥?紐낆묶??沅뚭퀬?⑸땲??</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-nameCheck" checked>
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Custom User Dictionary -->
          <div class="settings-section">
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
              <h4 class="settings-section-title" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                <i data-lucide="book-open"></i>
                <span>?섎쭔???⑥뼱 ?ъ쟾 (?덉쇅 諛?吏곸젒 異붽?)</span>
              </h4>
              <button class="btn" id="btn-add-dict-row">
                <i data-lucide="plus"></i>
                <span>?ъ쟾 ??ぉ 異붽?</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px;">
              ?ъ슜?먭? 異붽????⑥뼱?ㅼ? 湲곗옱 吏移??먭? ???곗꽑 諛섏쁺?⑸땲?? ?泥댁뼱 移몄쓣 鍮꾩썙?먮㈃(?먮뒗 ?덉쇅 泥섎━?섎㈃) 湲곕낯 ?ъ쟾???ㅻ쪟 紐⑸줉?먯꽌 ?덉쇅濡??쒖쇅?⑸땲??
            </p>

            <div class="dictionary-grid" id="custom-dictionary-list">
              <div class="dictionary-row" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 4px;">
                <span>李얠쓣 ?⑥뼱 (?ㅻ쪟 ?⑥뼱)</span>
                <span>?泥댄븷 ?⑥뼱 (?쒖븞)</span>
                <span>?댁쑀 / ?ㅻ챸</span>
                <span style="width: 28px;"></span>
              </div>
              <!-- Rows will be dynamically added here -->
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Google Gemini AI API 연동 -->
          <div class="settings-section" style="margin-top: 24px;">
            <h4 class="settings-section-title">
              <i data-lucide="brain-circuit"></i>
              <span>Google Gemini AI 점검 연동 (옵션)</span>
            </h4>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px;">
              로컬 사전을 보완하여 정적인 매칭으로 잡지 못하는 문맥 오류(우회 대학명 언급, 부모의 사회적 지위 암시 등)를 인공지능이 추가 정밀 분석합니다. 개인 식별 정보는 마스킹 처리 후 본문만 전송되므로 안전합니다.
            </p>
            
            <div class="toggle-item" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
              <div class="toggle-details">
                <h5>AI 점검 기능 활성화</h5>
                <p>Gemini API를 활용하여 문맥 기반 정밀 생기부 검사를 함께 수행합니다.</p>
              </div>
              <label class="switch">
                <input type="checkbox" id="setting-ai-enabled">
                <span class="slider"></span>
              </label>
            </div>

            <div class="editor-field-group" style="display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; width: 100%;">
              <span class="editor-label" style="width: 120px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px;">Gemini API Key</span>
              <input type="password" id="setting-ai-key" class="editor-input" style="flex: 1; height:32px; font-size:13px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; padding: 4px 8px; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text-primary);" placeholder="AI Studio에서 발급받은 API 키를 입력하세요">
              <button id="btn-save-ai-key" class="btn-primary" style="height: 32px; padding: 0 16px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; cursor: pointer; border: none; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white;">
                저장
              </button>
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-left: 3px solid var(--color-slang-text); border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
              💡 <b>[필독] 404 (Not Found) 오류 발생 시 자가 조치법</b><br>
              구글 AI Studio에서 API 키를 만드실 때, 기존 프로젝트가 아닌 <b>[새 프로젝트에서 API 키 만들기 (Create API key in new project)]</b>를 클릭하여 완전 새로운 프로젝트의 키를 생성해 등록해 주세요. 기존 기본 프로젝트(Default Gemini Project)에 권한 꼬임이 있을 때 발생하는 구글 클라우드 고유의 차단 버그를 100% 즉시 해결해 줍니다.
            </div>
          </div>



        </div>
      </div>


      
            
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; background-color: var(--bg-secondary); border-left: 3px solid var(--color-slang-text); border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">
              💡 <b>[필독] 404 (Not Found) 오류 발생 시 자가 조치법</b><br>
              구글 AI Studio에서 API 키를 만드실 때, 기존 프로젝트가 아닌 <b>[새 프로젝트에서 API 키 만들기 (Create API key in new project)]</b>를 클릭하여 완전 새로운 프로젝트의 키를 생성해 등록해 주세요. 기존 기본 프로젝트(Default Gemini Project)에 권한 꼬임이 있을 때 발생하는 구글 클라우드 고유의 차단 버그를 100% 즉시 해결해 줍니다.
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- TAB 5: SUBJECT GROUP VIEW -->
      <div id="subject-group-view" class="tab-content">
        <div class="split-container">
          
          <!-- 좌측: 과목 목록 사이드바 (290px) -->
          <div class="sidebar-student-list" id="sidebar-subject-list">
            <div style="padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; position: relative;">
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; width: 100%;">
                <span style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-primary);">과목 목록 <span id="subject-list-count" style="color: var(--color-loanword-text); font-weight:700;">0</span>개</span>
                <button id="btn-collapse-subject-list" class="btn-icon" title="목록 접기" style="border: none; background: none; padding: 4px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                  <i data-lucide="chevrons-left" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
                </button>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 과목 이름 검색 -->
              <div class="search-box" style="margin-top: 4px;">
                <i data-lucide="search"></i>
                <input type="text" id="subject-search-input-tab" placeholder="과목 이름 검색..." style="font-size:12px;">
              </div>
              
              <!-- 학년도/학기/학년 필터 드롭다운 -->
              <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px; margin-top: 4px;">
                <select id="subject-filter-year" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 11px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                  <option value="all">전체 학년도</option>
                </select>
                <select id="subject-filter-term" class="editor-input" style="padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 11px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                  <option value="all">전체 학기</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div style="margin-top: 4px;">
                <select id="subject-filter-grade" class="editor-input" style="width: 100%; padding: 3px 8px; font-size: 11px; height: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                  <option value="all">전체 학년</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 세로 과목 리스트 (스크롤) -->
            <div id="subject-list-container" style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 6px;">
              <!-- 과목 아이템들이 동적으로 빌드됨 -->
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 우측: 과목 상세 및 수강 학생 카드 그리드 영역 -->
          <div class="editor-main-area" id="subject-main-area">
            
            <!-- 대기 상태 (선택된 과목이 없을 때 표시) -->
            <div id="subject-empty-state" style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: center; padding: 32px;">
              <i data-lucide="book-open" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; color: var(--border-focus); margin-bottom: 12px;"></i>
              <h4 style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text-primary);">선택된 과목 없음</h4>
              <p style="font-size: 13px; max-width: 320px;">좌측 목록에서 수강 학생들을 확인할 과목을 선택해 주세요.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 실제 카드 그리드 본문 (과목 선택 시 활성화) -->
            <div id="subject-active-container" style="display: none; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; overflow: hidden; padding: 16px;">
              <div class="student-selector-bar" style="margin-bottom: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; background-color: transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 0 0 12px 0; display: flex; align-items: center;">
                <div class="student-info-tag" style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                  <button id="btn-expand-subject-list" class="btn-icon" title="목록 펼치기" style="display: none; border: none; background: none; padding: 5px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 4px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); background-color: var(--bg-secondary);">
                    <i data-lucide="chevrons-right" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i>
                  </button>
                  <strong id="current-subject-title" style="font-size:16px; color: var(--text-primary);">과목 선택 없음</strong>
                  <span id="current-subject-meta" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: 8px;"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- 학생 카드 그리드 (스크롤) -->
              <div id="subject-student-cards-container" style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 4px;">
                <!-- 학생 카드들이 동적으로 렌더링됨 -->
              </div>
            </div>

          </div> <!-- subject-main-area 닫힘 -->
        </div> <!-- split-container 닫힘 -->
      </div>

    </main>

  </div>

  <!-- Hidden Excel Input Element -->
  <input type="file" id="excel-file-input" style="display: none;" accept=".xlsx, .xls, .csv">

  <!-- Toast Container -->
  <div id="toast-container"></div>

  <script src="checker.js"></script>
  <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
